    <script type="text/javascript">
     $ensure(function(){
        if (window.location.hash &amp;&amp; window.location.hash == '#_=_') {
            if (window.history &amp;&amp; history.pushState) {
                window.history.pushState("", document.title,
                    window.location.href.replace(location.hash,""));
            } else {
                // Prevent scrolling by storing the page's current scroll offset
                var scroll = {
                    top: document.body.scrollTop,
                    left: document.body.scrollLeft
                };
                window.location.hash = '';
                // Restore the scroll offset, should be flicker free
                document.body.scrollTop = scroll.top;
                document.body.scrollLeft = scroll.left;
            }
        }

        // method that scrolls the headlines to a certain position
        function scrollRelated(seconds) {
            window.jQueryAutoScroll.doScrollTo(25*parseInt(seconds));
        }

        var rev_names = {};
        for(var k in menu_names){
            for(var vi in menu_names[k]){
                var sg = menu_names[k][vi].replace(/s$/,'');rev_names[sg] = k;
                var pl=(sg+'s').replace(/ys$/,'ies');rev_names[pl] = k;
            }
        }
        var showMenu = ensure(function(activeMenu, activeItem, shown){
            if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Activating menu: "+activeMenu);
            // &lt;ul id='menu-name' class="submenu border_color tabtrigger"&gt;&lt;li id='#child-menu-id' class="active"&gt;&lt;a id='#opened-tab-id'&gt;
            // or
            // &lt;ul id='main_menu' class="tabtrigger"&gt;&lt;li id='#child-menu-id' class="current"&gt;&lt;a id='#opened-tab-id'&gt;

            var activeMenuElement = $('ul'+activeMenu);
            var parentMenuItem = $('ul.tabtrigger li[id='+activeMenu+']');
            var parentMenuElement = parentMenuItem.parents('ul');
            var parentMenuName = '#'+parentMenuElement.attr('id');
            if(parentMenuItem.length){
                if(activeMenu != '#main-menu'){
                    var isGoodMenu=activeMenuElement.find('li').length&gt;1;
                    if(isGoodMenu){
                        activeItem.addClass('current');
                        activeMenuElement.css('z-index', '100');
                    }
                    if(parentMenuName != '#undefined' &amp;&amp; parentMenuName != activeMenu){
                        showMenu(parentMenuName, parentMenuItem, shown);
                    }
                    // slide down in reverse order, from the topmost menu
                    if(isGoodMenu){
                        activeMenuElement.slideDown('fast');
                        shown.push(activeMenu);
                    }
                }else{
                    activeItem.addClass('current');
                }
            }else{
                activeItem.addClass('current');
            }
        });

        window.updateMenus = ensure(function(tab){
            if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("updateMenus for: "+tab);
            jQuery('#login .history').css('color',tab=='#history'?'#c00':'');
            // find active menu
            var menu_item = $('.submenu li:not([id]) a[id='+tab+']').parents('li'); // item with no submenu
            if(!menu_item.length){
                menu_item = $('.submenu li a[id='+tab+']').parents('li'); // any submenu item
            }
            if(!menu_item.length){
                menu_item = $('.tabtrigger li a[id='+tab+']').parents('li'); // main menu item
            }
            // reset all submenus selection
            $('.submenu.tabtrigger').children('li').removeClass('active');
            // reset main menu selection
            $('.tabtrigger').children('li').removeClass('current');
            // move all submenus back
            $('.submenu').css('z-index', '10');
            var shown = [];
            var menu_name = '#'+(menu_item.parents('ul').attr('id') || 'main-menu');
            if(menu_item &amp;&amp; menu_name != '#undefined'){
                showMenu(menu_name, menu_item, shown);
            }
            // slide all other submenus up
            var open_submenu = false;
            $('.submenu').each(function(n,el){
                if($.inArray('#'+el.id, shown) == -1){
                    $(el).css('z-index', '100').slideUp('fast');
                }else if($(el).find('li').length&lt;=1){
                    // never show menus with only one element
                }else{
                    $(el).css('z-index', '100');
                    open_submenu = true;
                }
            });
            if(open_submenu){
                $('.submenu-container').slideDown('fast');
            }else{
                $('.submenu-container').slideUp('fast');
            }
        });

window.lastHistory = '';
window.activeArea = '';
window.fsonload = null;
window.firstTimeActivate = true;

var matchNumber = function(x){
    return x &amp;&amp; x.match(/^\d+$/);
}

var matchDash = function(x){
    return x &amp;&amp; x.match(/^\d+(-\d+)?(,\d+(-\d+)?)*$/);
}

var matchPosition = function(x){
    return x &amp;&amp; x.match(/^(\d+:)?\d+:\d+$/);
}

var matchAction = function(x){
    return x &amp;&amp; x.match(/^(\d+:)?\d+:\d+(\-|\.\.)(\d+:)?\d+:\d+$/);
}

function parseDash(x){
    var parts = x.split(/,/g);
    var r = [];
    for(var i in parts){
        var p = parts[i];
        if(p.match('-')){
            var rg = p.split('-');
            for(var t=rg[0]; t&lt;=rg[1]; t++){
               r.push(t|0);
            }
                }else{
                    r.push(p|0);
                }
            }
            return r;
        }

        var parsePosition = function(x){
            var parts = x.split(/:/g);
            var pos = 0;
            for(var p in parts){
                pos = pos*60 + parseInt(parts[p].trim() || '0', 10);
            }
            return pos;
        }

        window.history_pp = 20;

        var renderPage = function(number, active){
            var page = '';
            if(number == active){
                page += ' &lt;span class="active"&gt;'+active+'&lt;/span&gt; ';
            }else{
                page += ' &lt;a href="#" onclick=\'activateTab("history", "'+number+'");return false;\'&gt;'+number+'&lt;/a&gt; ';
            }
            return page;
        }

        var historyTemplate = _.template('&lt;div class="history-div"&gt;'+
            '&lt;a href="&lt;%= url %&gt;"&gt;&lt;%= title %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;'+
            '&lt;span style="color:gray;font-size:90%"&gt;&lt;%= at %&gt;&lt;/span&gt;'+
            '&lt;/div&gt;');

        var myPlaylists = DynamicStream('my_playlists', 10, 'http://editor.wn.com/personal/?kind=pages',
            '&lt;div class="item-div l80"&gt;'+
            '&lt;% if(thumb.width &amp;&amp; !thumb.url.match("^/")) { %&gt;'+
            '&lt;img width="&lt;%= thumb.width %&gt;" height="&lt;%= thumb.height %&gt;" src="&lt;%= thumb.url %&gt;" class="thumb" /&gt;'+
            '&lt;% } else { %&gt;'+
            '&lt;img width="72" height="54" src="http://login.wn.com/media/images/empty-120x90.png" class="thumb" /&gt;'+
            '&lt;% } %&gt;&lt;div class="info"&gt;'+
            '&lt;a href="http://wn.com/u/&lt;%= owner %&gt;/&lt;%= query %&gt;"&gt;&lt;%= title %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt; '+
            '&lt;span style="color:gray;font-size:90%"&gt;&lt;%= edited_at %&gt; ago&lt;/span&gt;'+
            //'&lt;br/&gt;&lt;% if(typeof duration!=="undefined"){ %&gt;Duration: &lt;%= duration %&gt;&lt;% } %&gt;&lt;br/&gt;'+
            '&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');

        var myVideos = DynamicStream('my_videos', 20, 'http://login.wn.com/history/played/',
            '&lt;div class="item-div l80"&gt;'+
            '&lt;img width="72" height="54" src="http://i.ytimg.com/vi/&lt;%= video_id %&gt;/default.jpg" class="thumb" /&gt;'+
            '&lt;div class="info"&gt;'+
            '&lt;a href="http://wn.com/&lt;%= title %&gt;"&gt;&lt;%= title %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt; '+
            '&lt;span style="color:gray;font-size:90%"&gt;&lt;%= edited_at %&gt; ago&lt;/span&gt;'+
            //'&lt;br/&gt;&lt;% if(typeof duration!=="undefined"){ %&gt;Duration: &lt;%= duration %&gt;&lt;% } %&gt;&lt;br/&gt;'+
            '&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');

        var globalHistory = DynamicStream('global_history', 20, 'http://login.wn.com/recent/all/',
            '&lt;div class="item-div l1"&gt;'+
            '&lt;a href="&lt;%= url %&gt;"&gt;&lt;%= title %&gt;&lt;/a&gt;'+
            '&lt;/div&gt;')


        var renderHistory = ensure(function(result){
            //pp = parseInt(result.pp);
            var stream = "";
            for(i in result.stream){
                var item = result.stream[i];
                var context = {
                    title: item.title,
                    url: item.url,
                    at: item.at_rel,
                };
                stream += historyTemplate(context);
            }
            $('#history .stream').html(stream);
            var page = result.page;
            if(result.pages&gt;1){
                var pages = '';
                pages += renderPage(1, page);
                if(result.nearby &amp;&amp; result.nearby[0]&gt;2){
                    pages += '...';
                }
                for(p in result.nearby){
                    pages += renderPage(result.nearby[p], page);
                }
                if(result.nearby &amp;&amp; result.nearby.slice(-1)[0]&lt;result.pages-1){
                    pages += ' ... ';
                }
                if(result.pages&gt;1){
                    pages += renderPage(result.pages, page);
                }
                //pages = pages + "(" + result.count;
            }else{
                pages = ''
            }
            $('.pagination').html('&lt;p&gt;'+pages+'&lt;/p&gt;');
            $('.stream &gt; div:odd').addClass('bgr_color');
            updateHeight('#history');
        });

        window.activateTabArea = ensure(function(tab, areas){
            var parsed = false;
            var parts = (areas || '').split('/');
            window.fsonload = jQuery.inArray('fs', parts) &gt;= 0;
            if(fsonload){
                parts.splice(parts.indexOf('fs'), 1);
            }
            var replayMode = false;
            if(jQuery.inArray('replay', parts)&gt;=0){
                replayMode = 'replay';
            }
            var previewMode = null;
            if(jQuery.inArray('p', parts)&gt;=0){
                previewMode = 'p';
            }
            if(jQuery.inArray('preview', parts)&gt;=0){
                previewMode = 'preview';
            }
            if(jQuery.inArray('repeat', parts)&gt;=0){
                replayMode = 'repeat';
            }
            if(jQuery.inArray('r', parts)&gt;=0 || jQuery.inArray('ro', parts)&gt;=0){
                replayMode = 'r';
            }
            if(replayMode){
                parts.splice(parts.indexOf(replayMode), 1);
            }
            if(previewMode){
                parts.splice(parts.indexOf(previewMode), 1);
            }
            if(previewMode){
                if(!parts.length){
                    parts = ['1-14', '999:59'];
                }
            }

            var area = parts[0];

            if(tab == 'history'){
                var page = parseInt(area || '1') || 1;
                jQuery.ajax({
                    url: 'http://login.wn.com/recent/json/?pp='+history_pp+'&amp;skip='+history_pp*(page-1),
                    dataType: 'jsonp',
                    success: function(response){
                        $ensure(function(){
                            renderHistory(response, page);
                        });
                    }
                });
                return true;
            }

            if(tab == 'global_history'){
                var page = parseInt(area || '1') || 1;
                globalHistory.fetchStream(page, '', function(){
                    updateHeight('#global_history');
                });
                return true;
            }

            if(tab == 'my_playlists'){
                var page = parseInt(area || '1') || 1;
                myPlaylists.fetchStream(page, '', function(){
                    updateHeight('#my_playlists');
                });
                return true;
            }

            if(tab == 'my_videos'){
                var page = parseInt(area || '1') || 1;
                myVideos.fetchStream(page, '', function(){
                    updateHeight('#my_videos');
                });
                return true;
            }

            if(tab == 'related_sites' &amp;&amp; areas &amp;&amp; matchPosition(areas)){
                var seconds = parsePosition(areas);
                scrollRelated(seconds);
                return false;
            }

            if(matchPosition(area) || matchAction(area)){
                parts.unshift('1');
                area = parts[0];
            }

            if(tab == 'expand' &amp;&amp; area &amp;&amp; area.match(/\d+/)) {
                var num = parseInt(area);
                if(num &lt; 100){
                    //FIX ME. Load news page with ajax here
                }
                else if(num &gt; 1900){
                    //FIX ME. Load timeline page with ajax here
                }
            }
            else if(tab.match(/^playlist\d+$/)){
                var playerId = parseInt(tab.substring(8));
                var vp = videoplayers[playerId];
                if(replayMode){
                    $('.replaycurrent'+playerId).attr('checked', true);
                    vp.setReplayCurrent(true);
                }
                var sources = {'yt': 'youtube', 'vm': 'vimeo', 'dm': 'dailymotion'};
                var findMatchingVideo = function(vid){
                    vid = vid.replace(/\/+$/,'');
                    if(vid.match(/^\d+$/)){
                        var number = parseInt(vid);
                        var pl = vp.getActualPlaylist();
                        return pl[number-1];
                    }else if(vid.match(/^\w\w-/)){
                        var pl = vp.getActualPlaylist();
                        var s = sources[vid.substr(0, 2)];
                        for(v in pl){
                            if(pl[v].source == s &amp;&amp; pl[v].video_id == vid.substr(3)){
                                return pl[v];
                            }
                        }
                    }else{
                        if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log)
                            console.log('Warning: Bad video id format:' + vid);
                        return null;
                    }
                }

                var parseAction = function(x){
                    var video = null;
                    var start = 0;
                    var stop = null; // at the end of video
                    if(x.match(/\//)){
                        var vid_pos = x.split(/\//, 2);
                        x = vid_pos[0];
                        var positions = vid_pos[1].split(/\-|\.\./, 2);
                        start = parsePosition(positions[0]) || 0;
                        if(positions[1] &amp;&amp; positions[1].trim()){
                            stop = parsePosition(positions[1]) || null;
                        }
                    }
                    video = findMatchingVideo(x);
                    return {
                        'video': video,
                        'start': start,
                        'stop': stop
                    };
                };

                var playQueue = [];
                window.playQueue = playQueue;
                var playQueuePosition = 0;
                var playShouldStart = null;
                var playShouldStop = null;
                var parseList = function(x){
                    var items = x.split(/;|,/g);
                    var results = [];
                    for (i in items){
                        try{
                            var action = parseAction(items[i]);
                            if(!action.video){
                                if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Warning: No video for queued entry: " + items[i]);
                            }else{
                                results.push(action);
                            }
                        }catch(e){
                            if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Warning: Can't parse queue entry: " + items[i]);
                        }
                    }
                    return results;
                };

                var scrollToPlaylistPosition = function(vp){
                    var ppos = vp.getPlaylistPosition();
                    var el = vp.playlistContainer.find('&gt;li').eq(ppos);
                    var par = el.closest('.playlist_scrollarea');
                    par.scrollTop(el.offset().top-par.height()/2);
                }

                var playQueueUpdate = function(){
                    var playPosition = playQueue[playQueuePosition];
                    vp.playFromPlaylist(playPosition.video);
                    scrollToPlaylistPosition(vp);
                    playShouldStart = playPosition.start;
                    playShouldStop = playPosition.stop;
                };

                var playQueueAdvancePosition = function(){
                    if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Advancing play position...");
                    playQueuePosition ++;
                    if(playQueuePosition &lt; playQueue.length){
                        playQueueUpdate();
                    }else if(vp.getReplayCurrent()){
                        playQueuePosition = 0;
                        playQueueUpdate();
                        vp.seekTo(playShouldStart);
                        vp.playVideo();
                    }else{
                        vp.pauseVideo();
                        playShouldStop = null;
                        playShouldStart = null;
                    }
                };

               function loadMoreVideos(playerId, vp, start, finish, callback){
                        var playlistInfo = playlists[playerId-1];
                        if(playlistInfo.loading &gt;= finish) return;
                        playlistInfo.loading = finish;
                        jQuery.ajax({
                            url: '/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/query_videos2',
                            dataType: 'json',
                            data: {
                                query: playlistInfo.query,
                                orderby: playlistInfo.orderby,
                                start: start,
                                count: finish-start
                            },
                            success: function(response){
                                var pl = vp.getPlaylist().slice(0);
                                pl.push.apply(pl, response);
                                vp.setPlaylist(pl);
                                callback();
                            }
                        });
               }

               if(parts.length == 1 &amp;&amp; matchDash(parts[0])){
                    var pl = vp.getActualPlaylist();
                    var vids = parseDash(parts[0]);
                    parts = [];
                    for(var i = 0; i &lt; vids.length; i++){
                        playQueue.push({
                            'video': pl[vids[i]-1],
                            'start': 0,
                            'stop': null
                        })
                    }
                    if(vids.length){
                        if(vids[vids.length-1]-1&gt;=pl.length){
                            loadMoreVideos(playerId, vp, pl.length, vids[vids.length-1], function(){
                                if(fsonload){
                                    activateTabArea(tab, parts[0]+'/fs');
                                }else{
                                    activateTabArea(tab, parts[0]);
                                }
                                var pls = vp.getPlaylist();
                                vp.playFromPlaylist(pls[pls.length-1]);
                                vp.playVideo();
                                scrollToPlaylistPosition(vp);
                            });
                            return true;
                        }
                    }
                    if(playQueue){
                        playQueueUpdate();
                        vp.playVideo();
                        parsed = true;
                        playShouldStart = 0;
                    }
               }

               if(previewMode){
                    var vids = [];
                    var dur = 0;
                    var pl = vp.getActualPlaylist();
                    area = parts[0];
                    if(parts.length == 1 &amp;&amp; matchPosition(parts[0])){
                        vids = parseDash('1-'+pl.length);
                        dur = parsePosition(parts[0]);
                        parts = [];
                    }else
                    if(parts.length == 1 &amp;&amp; matchDash(parts[0])){
                        vids = parseDash(parts[0]);
                        dur = parsePosition("999:59");
                        parts = [];
                    }
                    if(parts.length == 2 &amp;&amp; matchDash(parts[0]) &amp;&amp; matchPosition(parts[1])){
                        vids = parseDash(parts[0]);
                        dur = parsePosition(parts[1]);
                        parts = [];
                    }
                    for(var i = 0; i &lt; vids.length; i++){
                        playQueue.push({
                            'video': pl[vids[i]-1],
                            'start': 0,
                            'stop': dur
                        })
                    }
                    if(playQueue){
                        playQueueUpdate();
                        vp.playVideo();
                        parsed = true;
                    }
                }

                if(area){
                    var sel = findMatchingVideo(area);
                    if(sel){
                        vp.playFromPlaylist(sel);
                        playShouldStart = 0;
                        parsed = true;
                    }
                }

                if(fsonload || replayMode){
                    playShouldStart = 0;
                }

                if(document.location.search.match('at=|queue=')){
                    var opts = document.location.search.replace(/^\?/,'').split(/&amp;/g);
                    for(var o in opts){
                        if(opts[o].match(/^at=(\d+:)?(\d+:)?\d+$/)){
                            playShouldStart = parsePosition(opts[o].substr(3))
                        }
                        if(opts[o].match(/^queue=/)){
                            playQueue = parseList(opts[o].substr(6));
                            if(playQueue){
                                playQueuePosition = 0;
                                playQueueUpdate();
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }

                if(matchPosition(parts[1])){
                        playShouldStart = parsePosition(parts[1]);
                        parsed = true;
                }

                if(matchAction(parts[1])){
                        var action = parseAction(area+'/'+parts[1]);
                        playShouldStart = action.start;
                        playShouldStop = action.stop;
                        parsed = true;
                }

                if(playShouldStart !== null &amp;&amp; !playQueue.length){
                    playQueue.push({
                        video: vp.getCurrentVideo(),
                        start: playShouldStart,
                        stop: playShouldStop
                    });
                }

                if(playShouldStart != null){
                    setInterval(function(){
                        if(playShouldStop &amp;&amp; vp.currentPlayer &amp;&amp; vp.currentPlayer.getCurrentTime() &gt; playShouldStop){
                            playShouldStop = null;
                            if(vp.getCurrentVideo() == playQueue[playQueuePosition].video){
                                playQueueAdvancePosition();
                            }else{
                                playShouldStart = null;
                            }
                        }
                    }, 500);
                    vp.playerContainer.bind('videoplayer.player.statechange', function(e, state){
                        if(state == 'ended'){ // advance to the next video
                            playQueueAdvancePosition();
                        }
                    });
                    vp.playerContainer.bind('videoplayer.player.readychange', function(e, state){
                        if(state){
                            if(playShouldStart !== null){
                                vp.seekTo(playShouldStart);
                                playShouldStart = null;
                            }else{
                                playShouldStop = null; // someone started other video, stop playing from playQueue
                            }
                        }
                        if(fsonload) {
                            triggerFullscreen(playerId); fsonload = false;
                        }
                    });
                }
            }
            else if(tab.match(/^wiki\d+$/)){
                if(firstTimeActivate){
                    load_wiki($('#'+tab), function(){
                        if(area){
                            var areaNode = $('#'+area);
                            if(areaNode.length&gt;0){
                                $('html, body').scrollTop(areaNode.offset().top + 10);
                                return true;
                            }
                        }
                    });
                }
            }
            return parsed;
        })

        window.activateTab = ensure(function(tab, area){
            window.activeArea = null;
            if(tab == 'import_videos'){
                if(area){
                    import_videos(area);
                }else{
                    start_import();
                }
                return true;
            }
            if(tab == 'chat'){
                tab = 'videos';
                area = 'chat';
            }
            if(tab in rev_names){
                tab = rev_names[tab];
            }
            if(tab.match(':')){ return false; }
            var sup = $('ul li a[id=#'+tab+']');
            if(sup &amp;&amp; sup.length&gt;0){
                window.activeArea = area;
                sup.first().click();
                if(area == 'chat'){
                        open_subtab($('#'+tab).find('ul.tabs li[data-tab=tab-2]'));
                        update_chat_position($('#'+tab).find('ul.tabs .current'));
                }
                if(!window.activateTabArea(tab, area)){
                    window.activeArea = null;
                }
                window.activeArea = null;
                return true;
            }else{
                var have_tabs = $('#playlist_menu li').length;
                if(tab.match(/^playlists?\d+$/)){
                    var to_add = +tab.substring(8).replace(/^s/,'')-have_tabs;
                    if(to_add&gt;0){
                        add_more_videos(to_add);
                        return true;
                    }
                }
            }
            return false;
        });
        window.currentPath = ensure(function(){
            return window.lastHistory.replace(basepath, '').split('?')[0];
        });

        window.addHistory = ensure(function(path){
            if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Adding to history: "+path);
            if(window.history &amp;&amp; history.replaceState &amp;&amp; document.location.hostname.match(/^(\w{2,3}\.)?wn\.com$/)){
                if(path == 'videos' || path == 'videos/' || path == '' || path == '/') {
                    path = basepath;
                } else if( path.match('^videos/') ){
                    path = basepath + '/' + path.replace('videos/', '').replace('--','/');
                } else {
                    path = basepath + '/' + path.replace('--','/');
                }
                if(document.location.search){
                    path += document.location.search;
                }
                if(window.lastHistory) {
                    history.pushState(null, null, path);
                }
                else if(window.lastHistory != path){
                    history.replaceState(null, null, path);
                    window.lastHistory = path;
                }
            }
            else{
                path = path.replace('--','/');
                if(path == 'videos' || path == 'videos/' || path == '' || path == '/') {
                    path = '';
                }
                if(window.lastHistory != '/'+path){
                    window.location.hash = path? '/'+path : '';
                    window.lastHistory = '/'+path;
                }
            }
        });
        $('.tabtrigger li a').live('click', ensure(function() {
            var tab = $(this).attr('id');
            if(tab.substring(0,1) == '#'){
                var name = tab.substring(1);
                if(name in menu_names){
                    name = menu_names[name][0];
                }
                if(window.console &amp;&amp; console.log) console.log("Triggering tab: "+name+(window.activeArea?" activeArea="+window.activeArea:''));
                var path = name;
                if(window.activeArea){
                    path = path + '/' + window.activeArea;
                }
                if(tab.match(/playlist/)){
                        jQuery('#top_tools .multi-fullscreen').hide().delay(500);
                        update_chat_position($(tab).find('ul.tabs .current'));
                }else {
                       $('#chat-box').hide();
                       $('#top_tools .multi-fullscreen').show();
                }
                if(tab.match(/#playlist\d+/) || tab.match(/#details\d+/)){
                        $('.multiple-playlists').show();
                        $('.related_playlist').show();
                        $('.longest_videos_playlist').show();
                }else {
                        $('.multiple-playlists').hide();
                        $('.related_playlist').hide();
                        $('.longest_videos_playlist').hide();
                }

                // start the related script only when the tab is on screen showing
                if (tab.match(/related_sites/)) {
                    if (mc) {
                        mc.startCredits();
                    }
                }

                addHistory(path);
                setTimeout(ensure(function(){
                    if(tab.match(/language--/)){
                        jQuery('.tabtrigger').offscreentabs('activateTab', 'language');
                    }
                    if(tab.match(/weather/)) {
                     jQuery('.tabtrigger').offscreentabs('activateTab', 'weather');
                     loadContinent();
                    }
                    if(tab.match(/playlist/)){
                            update_chat_position($(tab).find('ul.tabs .current'));
                    }else {
                           $('#chat-box').hide();
                    }
                    updateMenus(tab);
                    updateHeight();
                }), 10);
            }
            return false;
        }));

        jQuery('.tabtrigger').offscreentabs({container: '#tabcontainer'});
        var parts = document.location.hash.replace(/[#\/]*/,'').split('/');
        var switches = parts.slice(1).join('/');
        if(matchDash(parts[0]) || matchNumber(parts[0]) || matchAction(parts[0]) || matchPosition(parts[0]) || parts[0].match(/^(fs|r|p|preview|replay|repeat)$/)){
             // missing 'video'
            activateTab('playlist1', parts.join('/'));
        }
        else if(parts[1] &amp;&amp; activateTab(parts[0]+'--'+parts[1]));
        else if(parts[0] &amp;&amp; activateTab(parts[0], switches));
        else if(activateTab('playlist1'));
        else activateTab('expand');
        firstTimeActivate = false;
    });
    </script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
     $(document).bind('videoplayback.repeat', function(e, playerContainer){
            $.each(videoplayers, function(i, vp){
                if(vp &amp;&amp; vp.playerContainer == playerContainer){
                    var info=vp.getActualPlaylist()[vp.getPlaylistPosition()];
                    $.ajax({
                        url: 'http://login.wn.com/videos/star/',
                        data:{
                            title: info.title,
                            video: info.source+':'+info.video_id,
                        },
                        dataType: 'jsonp',
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    </script>
    <div class="clearfix">
    </div>

    cursor: pointer;
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out 0s;
    z-index: 10;

    height: 36px;
    width: 40px;

    left: 115px;

    display: block;

    opacity: 1;

}

    height: 70px;
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    background: #222222 url("http://cdn8.wn.com/or/images/anything/wn_logo.png") no-repeat 45px 25px;
}#popup-widget .header{
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #CE3760;
    position: absolute; 
    right: 45px;
    top: 32px;
}#popup-widget .buttons{
    width: 100%;
}#popup-widget .buttons a{
    display: block;
    width: 193px;
    margin-top: 25px;
    padding: 0px;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    height: 35px;
}#popup-widget .rightCol{
    float: right;
    text-align: right;
    width: 50%;
    padding-right: 45px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    vertical-align: top;
}#popup-widget .leftCol{
    float: left;
    width: 50%; 
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding-left: 45px;

    text-align: left;
}#popup-widget .buttons a.facebook{

}#popup-widget .buttons a.twitter{
    background: url("http://cdn7.wn.com/or/images/anything/twitterShare.png") no-repeat;
}#popup-widget .buttons a.google{
    background: url("http://cdn7.wn.com/or/images/anything/googleShare.png") no-repeat;
}
#popup-widget .rightCol a {
    float: right;
    top: 0px;
    position: relative !important;
    width: 193px;
}
#popup-widget .rightCol a.email{
    background: url("http://cdn0.wn.com/or/images/anything/emailShare.png") no-repeat top right;

}
 /*   TTip  */
   .custom_bgr .TTip {
      position: relative;
  }.custom_bgr .TTip span {
      background-color: #000000;
      border-radius: 3px;
      color: #ffffff;
      display: none;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.4em;
      margin-left: -5px;
      padding: 3px;
      position: absolute;
      text-align: center;
      top: 54px;
      width: 120px;
      z-index: 52;
  }.custom_bgr .TTip i {
      border-bottom: 4px solid #000000;
      border-left: 4px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
      border-right: 4px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
      height: 0;
      left: 50px;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      position: absolute;
      top: -4px;
      width: 0;display: none;
  }.custom_bgr .TTip:hover span {
      display: block;

      width: 85px;

      left: 70px;

   <script type="text/javascript">
    &lt;!--
    function load_city_info(city) {
            jQuery.ajax({
            url: '/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/wikipedia',
            data: {'query': city},
            success: function(text) {
                var aTag = $("a[name='city_wiki']");
                $('.city-data .city_wiki').find('.content').html(jQuery(text));
                $('html,body').animate({scrollTop: aTag.offset().top},'fast');

                }
        });
    }
    function load_videos(city){
                query = city + 'city'
                jQuery.ajax({
                url: '/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/video_results',
                data: {'query': city },
                success: function(text){
                    jQuery('.city-data .video-results').find('.content').html(jQuery(text));
                    }
                });
    }
    function load_video_details(query, id){
                jQuery('#details'+id).find('.moreDetails').html('&lt;p&gt;loading...&lt;/p&gt;');
                jQuery.ajax({
                url: '/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/video_details',
                data: {'query': query },
                success: function(text){
                    jQuery('#details'+id).find('.moreDetails').html(jQuery(text));
                    }
                });
    }
    function load_news(city){
                query = city + 'city'
                jQuery.ajax({
                url: '/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/news_headlines',
                data: {'query': city },
                success: function(text){
                    jQuery('.city-data .news-results').find('.content').html(jQuery(text));
                    }
                });
    }
          var find_video_andplayfs = ensure(function(query) {
               // search youtube for first match
               jQuery.ajax({
                   data: {
                       t: 'cheetah-photo-search/mvs_videosearch.txt',
                       query: query,
                     },
                   dataType: 'jsonp',
                   url: 'http://upge.wn.com/',
                   success: function(text) {
                       videoplayer_fs.clearPlaylist();
                       video_to_add = $(text).find('.video-info').first();
                       if (video_to_add.length &gt; 0) {
                                videoplayer_fs.addVideo(video_to_add);
                                videoplayer_fs.playlistContainer.find('li').last().find('a.playlistitem').click();
                                 $('html, body').animate({scrollTop:0}, 'slow');
                                triggerFullscreen(1);
                       }
                       else {
                           $('#noresults').html('&lt;span data-trans="Could not find a suitable video!"&gt;Could not find a suitable video!&lt;/span&gt;');
                       }
                   }
               });
               return false;
           });

     // --&gt;
   </script>

                            function share_popup(video_title, video_url){
                jQuery('#popup-widget').find('.buttons').html('&lt;div class="leftCol"&gt;&lt;a href="http://twitter.com/home?status=' +video_title+ '" class="twitter" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=' +video_title+ '" class="facebook" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=' +video_title+ '" class="google" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="rightCol"&gt;&lt;a onclick="return load_iframe_url(this.id, this.href)" data-reveal-id="footer-iframe" id="footer_iframe" class="sms close-reveal-modal" href="http://wn.com/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/sms_popup?title=' +video_title+ '&amp;url=' +video_url+ '"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a onclick="return load_iframe_url(this.id, this.href)" data-reveal-id="footer-iframe" id="footer_iframe" class="email close-reveal-modal" href="http://wn.com/api/upge/cheetah-photo-search/email_popup?title=' +video_title+ '&amp;url=' +video_url+ '"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;');
                jQuery('.iframe').hide();
            }
    
    
                function open_in_new_tab(url)
                {
                  window.open(url, '_blank');
                  window.focus();
                }
                function triggerLoadFile(file){
                    var file_name = file;
                    jQuery('#writers .byNames').find('.column-left').load('http://wn.com/api/upge/shared/' + file_name);
                    jQuery('.byNames').show().css('height', $('.byNames').height());
                    jQuery('.byCountry').hide();
                    updateHeight();
                }
                function triggerLoadList(file){
                var file_name = file;
                    jQuery('#writers').find('.byCountry').load('http://wn.com/api/upge/shared/' + file_name);
                    jQuery('.byNames').hide();
                    jQuery('.byCountry').show().css('height', $('.byCountry').height());
                    updateHeight();
                }
                function scrollToAnchor(aid){
                    var aTag = $("a[name='"+ aid +"']");
                    $('html,body').animate({scrollTop: aTag.offset().top},'slow');
                }

                            if(e.id == t.attr('id')){
                                pos = i;

                        });

                        var video_title = $('div.video-desc:eq('+pos+') div.video-title');

                var fullscreen_interval_caller = false;

                jQuery('.play-album-fullscreen').live('click', ensure(function(e) {
                    videoplayer_fs.clearPlaylist();

                    // checking if we have at least one video in the playlist in order to click it
                    fullscreen_interval_caller = setInterval(function(){
                        first_video = jQuery('#playlistcontainer_fs').find('a.playlistitem:first');
                        if (first_video) {
                            first_video.find('img.playlist-thumbnail').click();
                            triggerFullscreen(1);
                            clearInterval(fullscreen_interval_caller);
                        }
                    }, 1000);
                }));

                jQuery('.play-fullscreen').live('click', ensure(function(e) {
                    videoplayer_fs.clearPlaylist();
                    fullscreen_interval_caller = setInterval(function(){
                        first_video = videoplayer_fs.playlistContainer.find('li').first().find('a.playlistitem');
                        if (first_video) {
                            first_video.click();
                            triggerFullscreen(1);
                            clearInterval(fullscreen_interval_caller);
                        }
                    }, 1000);

                }));
        });

   <script>
    $(function(){
	
        var $title = $(".page_title");    
        var $numWords = $title.text().length;
        
        if (($numWords &gt;= 1) &amp;&amp; ($numWords &lt; 40)) {
            $title.css("font-size", "22px").css("margin-top", "3px");      
        }
        else if (($numWords &gt;= 10) &amp;&amp; ($numWords &lt; 70)) {
            $title.css("font-size", "20px").css("margin-top", "8px");
        }
        else if (($numWords &gt;= 15) &amp;&amp; ($numWords &lt; 100)) {
            $title.css("font-size", "18px").css("margin-top", "12px");
        }
        else if (($numWords &gt;= 100) &amp;&amp; ($numWords &lt; 125)) {
            $title.css("font-size", "14px").css("margin-top", "12px");
        }
        else {
            $title.css("font-size", "14px").css("margin-top", "0px").css("height", "2.8em").show();
        }    
        $(".page_title").show();   
        
        
    });
   </script>
   <script type="text/javascript">

            })
        });

   <script type="text/javascript">
    &lt;!--
        function open_subtab(el){
                var tab_id = $(el).attr('data-tab');
                    $('ul.tabs li').removeClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content').removeClass('current');
                $(el).addClass('current');
                    $('.tab-content').removeClass('current');
                    $("."+tab_id).addClass('current');
        }

        $ensure(function() {
                $('ul.tabs li').click(function(){
                    open_subtab(this);
                });

                $('#panelSlider').hover(function() {
                     $(this).stop(true, false).animate({'bottom': '0px'}, 900);
                     $(this).find('.fs-videos').css("background-image", "url(http://cdn1.wn.com/or/images/double-down-arrow.png)");


                }, function() {
                    $(this).stop(true, false).animate({'bottom': '-190px'}, 900);
                    $(this).find('.fs-videos').css("background-image", "url(http://cdn0.wn.com/or/images/double-up-arrow.png)");

                });


                $('#nav').hover(function() {
                            $('.nav.fsmode').stop(true, false).animate({'left': '0px'}, 900);
                            $('.nav.fsmode').css("background-image", "url(http://cdn8.wn.com/or/images/double-left-arrow.png)");
                        }, function() {
                            $('.nav.fsmode').animate({'left': '-180px'}, 900);
                            $('.nav.fsmode').css("background-image", "url(http://cdn3.wn.com/or/images/double-right-arrow.png)");

                });
                $('#panelButtons').hover(function() {
                    $(this).stop(true, false).animate({'top': '0px'}, 900);
                    $('.fs-button-switch').css('background-image', 'url(http://cdn0.wn.com/or/images/double-up-arrow.png)');
                    $('.fs-button').show();
                }, function() {
                    $(this).stop(true, false).animate({'top': '-27px'}, 900);
                    $('.fs-button-switch').css('background-image', 'url(http://cdn1.wn.com/or/images/double-down-arrow.png)');
                    $('.fs-button').hide();
                });

                /* esc fs mode on tab click */
                $('.fsmode li a').live('click', function() {
                    $('.fs-close').click();
                });
                /* esc fs mode on tab click */
                $('.fs-button.esc_fs').live('click', function() {
                    $('.fs-close').click();
                });



                $('.fs-button.playlist').click(function(){
                            var toggle_switch = $(this);
                              if(toggle_switch.html()=='Playlist'){
                                toggle_switch.html('Hide Playlist');
                                $('.playlistformating.fsmode').animate({'right': '0px'}, 900);
                              }else{
                                toggle_switch.html('Playlist');
                                $('.playlistformating.fsmode').animate({'right': '-365px'}, 900);
                              }
                });
                $('.fs-button.videos').click(function(){
                                var toggle_switch = $(this);
                              if(toggle_switch.html()=='Videos'){
                                toggle_switch.html('Hide Videos');
                                $('#panelSlider').animate({'bottom': '0px'}, 900);
                              }else{
                                toggle_switch.html('Videos');
                                $('#panelSlider').animate({'bottom': '-190px'}, 900);
                              }
                });
                $('.fs-button.menu').click(function(){
                             var toggle_switch = $(this);
                              if(toggle_switch.html()=='Menu'){
                                toggle_switch.html('Hide Menu');
                                $('.nav.fsmode').animate({'left': '0px'}, 900);
                              }else{
                                toggle_switch.html('Menu');
                                $('.nav.fsmode').animate({'left': '-180px'}, 900);
                              }
                });
                $('.fs-button.all').click(function(){
                             var toggle_switch = $(this);
                              if(toggle_switch.html()=='open all'){
                                toggle_switch.html('close all');
                                $('.fs-button.playlist').html('Hide Playlist');
                                $('.fs-button.videos').html('Hide Videos');
                                $('.fs-button.menu').html('Hide Menu');
                                $('.nav.fsmode').animate({'left': '0px'}, 900);
                                $('#panelSlider').animate({'bottom': '0px'}, 900);
                                $('.playlistformating.fsmode').animate({'right': '0px'}, 900);
                              }else{
                                toggle_switch.html('open all');
                                $('.fs-button.playlist').html('Playlist');
                                $('.fs-button.videos').html('Videos');
                                $('.fs-button.menu').html('Menu');
                                $('.nav.fsmode').animate({'left': '-180px'}, 900);
                                $('#panelSlider').animate({'bottom': '-190px'}, 900);
                                $('.playlistformating.fsmode').animate({'right': '-365px'}, 900);

                              }
                });


        });

                var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
                for(var i=0;i &lt; ca.length;i++) {
                    var c = ca[i];
                    while (c.charAt(0)==' ') c = c.substring(1,c.length);

                }
                return null;

var quantcast_host = function(){
    var h = document.location.hostname;
    if(h == 'wn.com') return 'main';
    if(h.match('^..\.wn\.com$')) return 'international';
    if(h.match('\.wn\.com$')) return 'subdomain';
    return 'outer';
}();

    var elem = document.createElement('script');
    elem.src = (document.location.protocol == "https:" ? "https://secure" : "http://edge") + ".quantserve.com/quant.js";
    elem.async = true;
    elem.type = "text/javascript";
    var scpt = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];
    scpt.parentNode.insertBefore(elem, scpt);
})();
